wikipedia_page.main: Catherine Mary Bakewell, Baroness Bakewell of Hardington Mandeville,  (born 7 March 1949), known as Cathy Bakewell, is a British politician who is a Liberal Democrat member of the House of Lords and formerly an elected District Councillor for the Coker ward of South Somerset.
